      "content": "groups don't stop the nerves from firing or the burning from happening. they just give me people to complain to, but the reality is still the same when i'm alone. it feels like there's no real way out of this except to just stop being. is it really so wrong to just want to be done with the suffering? like, imagine if i could just find peace and not have to feel any of this anymore. wouldn't that be a mercy?",
